    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle has been maintained to an exacting standard, exhibiting a pristine aesthetic and flawless mechanical integrity. Every detail, from the lustrous exterior finish to the preserved interior surfaces, reflects a history of fastidious care. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle in truly showroom condition, offering a driving experience that remains indistinguishable from its original delivery state. We invite the most discerning buyers to inspect this exemplary unit.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
